==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Festal
<hw>Fes"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>festum</ets>
holiday, feast. See <er>feast</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to a
holiday or a feast; joyous; festive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>You bless with choicer wine the <qex>festal</qex> day.</q>
<rj><qau>Francis.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Festally</ent>⟦br⟧
